	(91,2,'2013-09-30 07:26:53','2013-09-30 07:26:53','OK, folks! This is it. We go public.\n\nWell, not that ‘public’ not yet, but quite openly we’ll present our product idea at the startup conference <a href=\"http://idcee.org/\">IDCEE 2013</a> in Keiv, 10-11 of October. What IDCEE is telling the world:\n\n<strong>IDCEE is a high-scale international gathering of investors, startups, leaders of IT-companies, geeks and bloggers in the heart of Europe</strong>\n\n<strong>IDCEE: your entry point to the emerging markets of CEE and CIS</strong>\n\n<strong>IDCEE: ideas matter</strong>\n\nWe’ll see. Reportedly the startup contest they run there is pure fake, Even so, the amount of attendees make it worth doing it. We have made an <a href=\"http://issuu.com/ihorstarepravo/docs/nebel.tv_-_executive_summary\">Exec Summary</a> for the competition. That was good exercise.\n\nLook forward to seeing people there. If you plan to attend, don’t hesitate to come and see us.\n\n<iframe src=\"//e.issuu.com/embed.html#4544509/5260919\" height=\"371\" width=\"525\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>','Attending IDCEE 2013 - Keiv, Startup Fair ','','publish','open','open','','attending-idcee-2013-keiv-startup-fair','','','2013-09-30 07:26:53','2013-09-30 07:26:53','',0,'http://www.nebel.tv/?p=46',0,'post','',0),
	(92,2,'2013-10-14 12:11:22','2013-10-14 12:11:22','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n<w:WordDocument>\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\n<w:TrackMoves/>\n<w:TrackFormatting/>\n<w:PunctuationKerning/>\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\n<w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\n<w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\n<w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\n<w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\n<w:Compatibility>\n<w:BreakWrappedTables/>\n<w:SnapToGridInCell/>\n<w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\n<w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\n<w:DontGrowAutofit/>\n<w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>\n<w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>\n<w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>\n<w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>\n<w:Word11KerningPairs/>\n<w:CachedColBalance/>\n</w:Compatibility>\n<m:mathPr>\n<m:mathFont m:val=\"Cambria Math\"/>\n<m:brkBin m:val=\"before\"/>\n<m:brkBinSub m:val=\"--\"/>\n<m:smallFrac m:val=\"off\"/>\n<m:dispDef/>\n<m:lMargin m:val=\"0\"/>\n<m:rMargin m:val=\"0\"/>\n<m:defJc m:val=\"centerGroup\"/>\n<m:wrapIndent m:val=\"1440\"/>\n<m:intLim m:val=\"subSup\"/>\n<m:naryLim m:val=\"undOvr\"/>\n</m:mathPr></w:WordDocument>\n</xml><![endif]-->\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Hallelujah! </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Nebel.TV’s very first public exposure is done! I’m very glad it is over as it makes me incredibly tired having to repeat the very same speech to all comers over and over again.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Although it is tiring, I must admit it drives motivation sky high. Once you see how people respond to your idea - whether they like it, what questions they ask - you become more and more sure that you are going in the right direction. I’m proud to say that, with maybe one or two exceptions, no one left without being impressed with Nebel.TV.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">What people particularly liked:</span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The ability to access media content everywhere overcoming network and format boundaries</span></li>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Pausing the live show and continue watching it later</span></li>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Seamlessly and privately sharing you media files with your friends</span></li>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Integrated ability to pay and get paid for your content</span></li>\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Follow your favorite artists with no intermediates (agents, labels, etc.) and support them directly</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">There were tons of the ideas I got by both explaining the features of Nebel.TV to others as well as some suggested by my audience.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Unfortunately we didn’t win the competition; we didn’t even get invited to the pitching session. Still, I think the exposure and information resonance was quite loud. I think at these kinds of events more attention has to be paid to visual aids which will invite and encourage people to see the project.  Still, as for our first experience of its kind it was greatly successful!</span></p>\n <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Now, here I am on the second day.</span>\n\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n<w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" DefUnhideWhenUsed=\"true\"\nDefSemiHidden=\